msgid "# GLM-4.5/4.6/4.7"
msgstr "# GLM-4.5/4.6/4.7"

msgid "## Introduction"
msgstr "## 简介"

msgid ""
"GLM-4.x series models use a Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) architecture and are "
"foundational models specifically designed for agent applications."
msgstr "GLM-4.x 系列模型采用混合专家（MoE）架构，是专为智能体应用设计的基础模型。"

msgid "The `GLM-4.5` model is first supported in `vllm-ascend:v0.10.0rc1`."
msgstr "`GLM-4.5` 模型在 `vllm-ascend:v0.10.0rc1` 中首次获得支持。"

msgid ""
"This document will show the main verification steps of the model, including "
"supported features, feature configuration, environment preparation, single-"
"node and multi-node deployment, accuracy and performance evaluation."
msgstr "本文档将展示该模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持的特性、特性配置、环境准备、单节点和多节点部署、精度及性能评估。"

msgid "## Supported Features"
msgstr "## 支持的特性"

msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the "
"model's supported feature matrix."
msgstr ""
"请参考[支持的特性](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取模型支持的特性矩阵。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [feature guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get the"
" feature's configuration."
msgstr "请参考[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性的配置方法。"

msgid "## Environment Preparation"
msgstr "## 环境准备"

msgid "### Model Weight"
msgstr "### 模型权重"

msgid ""
"- `GLM-4.5`(BF16 version): [Download model weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-4.5).\n"
"- `GLM-4.6`(BF16 version): [Download model weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-4.6).\n"
"- `GLM-4.7`(BF16 version): [Download model weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-4.7).\n"
"- `GLM-4.5-w8a8-with-float-mtp`(Quantized version with mtp): [Download model weight](https://modelers.cn/models/Modelers_Park/GLM-4.5-w8a8).\n"
"- `GLM-4.6-w8a8`(Quantized version without mtp): [Download model weight](https://modelers.cn/models/Modelers_Park/GLM-4.6-w8a8). Because vllm does not support GLM4.6 mtp in October, we do not provide an mtp version. Last month, it was supported; you can use the following quantization scheme to add mtp weights to the quantized weights.\n"
"- `GLM-4.7-w8a8-with-float-mtp`(Quantized version without mtp): [Download model weight](https://modelscope.cn/models/Eco-Tech/GLM-4.7-W8A8-floatmtp).\n"
"- `Method of Quantization`: [quantization scheme](https://ai.gitcode.com/Ascend-SACT/GLM-4.5-w8a8). You can use these methods to quantize the model."
msgstr ""
"- `GLM-4.5`（BF16版本）：[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-4.5)。\n"
"- `GLM-4.6`（BF16版本）：[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-4.6)。\n"
"- `GLM-4.7`（BF16版本）：[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-4.7)。\n"
"- `GLM-4.5-w8a8-with-float-mtp`（含mtp的量化版本）：[下载模型权重](https://modelers.cn/models/Modelers_Park/GLM-4.5-w8a8)。\n"
"- `GLM-4.6-w8a8`（不含mtp的量化版本）：[下载模型权重](https://modelers.cn/models/Modelers_Park/GLM-4.6-w8a8)。由于vllm在十月份不支持GLM4.6的mtp，我们未提供mtp版本。上个月已支持；您可以使用以下量化方案将mtp权重添加到量化权重中。\n"
"- `GLM-4.7-w8a8-with-float-mtp`（不含mtp的量化版本）：[下载模型权重](https://modelscope.cn/models/Eco-Tech/GLM-4.7-W8A8-floatmtp)。\n"
"- `量化方法`：[量化方案](https://ai.gitcode.com/Ascend-SACT/GLM-4.5-w8a8)。您可以使用这些方法对模型进行量化。"

msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to the shared directory of "
"multiple nodes, such as `/root/.cache/`."
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到多节点共享目录，例如 `/root/.cache/`。"

msgid "### Installation"
msgstr "### 安装"

msgid "You can use our official docker image to run `GLM-4.x` directly."
msgstr "您可以使用官方提供的Docker镜像直接运行 `GLM-4.x`。"

msgid "=== \"A3 series\""
msgstr "=== \"A3系列\""

msgid "Start the docker image on each node."
msgstr "在每个节点上启动Docker镜像。"

msgid "=== \"A2 series\""
msgstr "=== \"A2系列\""

msgid "Start the docker image on your each node."
msgstr "在您的每个节点上启动Docker镜像。"

msgid ""
"In addition, if you don't want to use the docker image as above, you can "
"also build all from source:"
msgstr "此外，如果您不想使用上述Docker镜像，也可以从源码全部构建："

msgid ""
"- Install `vllm-ascend` from source, refer to "
"[installation](../../installation.md)."
msgstr "- 从源码安装 `vllm-ascend`，请参考[安装指南](../../installation.md)。"

msgid ""
"If you want to deploy multi-node environment, you need to set up environment"
" on each node."
msgstr "如果您想部署多节点环境，需要在每个节点上配置环境。"

msgid "## Deployment"
msgstr "## 部署"

msgid "### Single-node Deployment"
msgstr "### 单节点部署"

msgid ""
"- In low-latency scenarios, we recommend a single-machine deployment.\n"
"- Quantized model `glm4.7_w8a8_with_float_mtp` can be deployed on 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) or 1 Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8)."
msgstr ""
"- 在低延迟场景下，我们推荐单机部署。\n"
"- 量化模型 `glm4.7_w8a8_with_float_mtp` 可部署在1台 Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）或1台 Atlas 800 A2（64G × 8）上。"

msgid "Run the following script to execute online inference."
msgstr "运行以下脚本执行在线推理。"

msgid ""
"**Notice:**\n"
"The parameters are explained as follows:"
msgstr ""
"**注意：**\n"
"参数说明如下："

msgid ""
"- `fusion_ops_gmmswigluquant` The performance of the GmmSwigluQuant fusion operator tends to degrade when the total number of NPUs is ≤ 16.\n"
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1` Due to the FD feature of the FIA operator being invalidated by padding data introduced by this feature, we recommend disabling the `flashcomm1` feature for long-sequence (≥16k) and low-concurrency (≤8 batch size) scenarios.For long-sequence and high-concurrency scenarios, you may enable this feature to achieve improved Prefill performance."
msgstr ""
"- `fusion_ops_gmmswigluquant`：当NPU总数 ≤ 16时，GmmSwigluQuant融合算子的性能可能会下降。\n"
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1`：由于该特性引入的填充数据会使FIA算子的FD特性失效，我们建议在长序列（≥16k）且低并发（≤8 batch size）场景下禁用 `flashcomm1` 特性。对于长序列且高并发场景，您可以启用此特性以获得更好的Prefill性能。"

msgid "### Multi-node Deployment"
msgstr "### 多节点部署"

msgid ""
"While the previous documentation advises against multi-node deployment on "
"the Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8) platform, this configuration can still be "
"implemented for the GLM-4.x model if required. To proceed with a dual-node "
"setup, execute the following scripts on each respective node."
msgstr ""
"尽管之前的文档不建议在 Atlas 800 A2（64G × "
"8）平台上进行多节点部署，但如有需要，仍可为GLM-4.x模型实施此配置。要进行双节点设置，请在各个节点上执行以下脚本。"

msgid "**Node 0**"
msgstr "**节点 0**"

msgid "**Node 1**"
msgstr "**节点 1**"

msgid "### Prefill-Decode Disaggregation"
msgstr "### Prefill-Decode分离部署"

msgid ""
"We'd like to show the deployment guide of `GLM-4.7` on multi-node "
"environment with 2P1D for better performance."
msgstr "我们将展示 `GLM-4.7` 在多节点环境下采用2P1D配置以获得更好性能的部署指南。"

msgid "Before you start, please"
msgstr "开始之前，请"

msgid "1. prepare the script `launch_online_dp.py` on each node:"
msgstr "1. 在每个节点上准备脚本 `launch_online_dp.py`："

msgid "2. prepare the script `run_dp_template.sh` on each node."
msgstr "2. 在每个节点上准备脚本 `run_dp_template.sh`。"

msgid ""
"Once the preparation is done, you can start the server with the following "
"command on each node:"
msgstr "准备工作完成后，您可以在每个节点上使用以下命令启动服务器："

msgid "1. Prefill node 0"
msgstr "1. Prefill节点 0"

msgid "2. Prefill node 1"
msgstr "2. Prefill节点 1"

msgid "3. Decode node 0"
msgstr "3. Decode节点 0"

msgid "4. Decode node 1"
msgstr "4. Decode节点 1"

msgid "### Request Forwarding"
msgstr "### 请求转发"

msgid ""
"To set up request forwarding, run the following script on any machine. You "
"can get the proxy program in the repository's examples: "
"[load_balance_proxy_server_example.py](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/examples/disaggregated_prefill_v1/load_balance_proxy_server_example.py)"
msgstr ""
"要设置请求转发，请在任意机器上运行以下脚本。您可以在仓库的示例中获取代理程序：[load_balance_proxy_server_example.py](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/examples/disaggregated_prefill_v1/load_balance_proxy_server_example.py)"

msgid "## Functional Verification"
msgstr "## 功能验证"

msgid ""
"Once your server is started, you can query the model with input prompts:"
msgstr "服务器启动后，您可以使用输入提示词查询模型："

msgid "## Accuracy Evaluation"
msgstr "## 精度评估"

msgid "Here are two accuracy evaluation methods."
msgstr "这里提供两种精度评估方法。"

msgid ""
"1. Refer to [Using "
"AISBench](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md) for details."
msgstr ""
"1. 详情请参考[使用AISBench](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md)。"

msgid ""
"2. After execution, you can get the result, here is the result of `GLM-4.7` "
"in `vllm-ascend:main` (after `vllm-ascend:0.14.0rc1`) for reference only."
msgstr ""
"2. 执行后，您可以获得结果，以下是 `GLM-4.7` 在 `vllm-ascend:main`（`vllm-ascend:0.14.0rc1` "
"之后）上的结果，仅供参考。"

msgid ""
"| dataset | version | metric | mode | vllm-api-general-chat | note |\n"
"|----- | ----- | ----- | ----- | -----| ----- |\n"
"| GPQA | - | accuracy | gen | 84.85 | 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) |\n"
"| MATH500 | - | accuracy | gen | 98.8 | 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) |"
msgstr ""
"| 数据集 | 版本 | 指标 | 模式 | vllm-api-general-chat | 备注 |\n"
"|----- | ----- | ----- | ----- | -----| ----- |\n"
"| GPQA | - | 准确率 | 生成 | 84.85 | 1台 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) |\n"
"| MATH500 | - | 准确率 | 生成 | 98.8 | 1台 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) |"

msgid "### Using Language Model Evaluation Harness"
msgstr "### 使用语言模型评估工具"

msgid "Not tested yet."
msgstr "尚未测试。"

msgid "## Performance"
msgstr "## 性能"

msgid "### Using AISBench"
msgstr "### 使用AISBench"

msgid ""
"Refer to [Using AISBench for performance "
"evaluation](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md#execute-"
"performance-evaluation) for details."
msgstr ""
"详情请参考[使用AISBench进行性能评估](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md#execute-"
"performance-evaluation)。"

msgid "### Using vLLM Benchmark"
msgstr "### 使用vLLM基准测试"

msgid "Run performance evaluation of `GLM-4.x` as an example."
msgstr "以`GLM-4.x`的性能评估为例。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [vllm benchmark](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/benchmarking/) for "
"more details."
msgstr "更多详情请参考[vllm基准测试](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/benchmarking/)。"

msgid "There are three `vllm bench` subcommands:"
msgstr "`vllm bench`包含三个子命令："

msgid ""
"- `latency`: Benchmark the latency of a single batch of requests.\n"
"- `serve`: Benchmark the online serving throughput.\n"
"- `throughput`: Benchmark offline inference throughput."
msgstr ""
"- `latency`：对单批次请求的延迟进行基准测试。\n"
"- `serve`：对在线服务吞吐量进行基准测试。\n"
"- `throughput`：对离线推理吞吐量进行基准测试。"

msgid "Take the `serve` as an example. Run the code as follows."
msgstr "以`serve`为例，运行如下代码。"

msgid ""
"After about several minutes, you can get the performance evaluation result."
msgstr "大约几分钟后，即可获得性能评估结果。"

msgid "## Best Practices"
msgstr "## 最佳实践"

msgid "In this chapter, we recommend best practices for three scenarios:"
msgstr "本章针对三种场景推荐最佳实践："

msgid ""
"- Long-context: For long sequences with low concurrency (≤ 4): set `dp1 tp16`; For long sequences with high concurrency (> 4): set `dp2 tp8`\n"
"- Low-latency: For short sequences with low latency: we recommend setting `dp2 tp8`\n"
"- High-throughput: For short sequences with high throughput: we also recommend setting `dp2 tp8`"
msgstr ""
"- 长上下文：对于低并发（≤ 4）的长序列：设置`dp1 tp16`；对于高并发（> 4）的长序列：设置`dp2 tp8`\n"
"- 低延迟：对于低延迟的短序列：建议设置`dp2 tp8`\n"
"- 高吞吐量：对于高吞吐量的短序列：同样建议设置`dp2 tp8`"

msgid ""
"**Notice:**\n"
"`max-model-len` and `max-num-seqs` need to be set according to the actual usage scenario. For other settings, please refer to the **[Deployment](#deployment)** chapter."
msgstr ""
"**注意：**\n"
"`max-model-len`和`max-num-seqs`需要根据实际使用场景进行设置。其他设置请参考**[部署](#deployment)**章节。"

msgid "## FAQ"
msgstr "## 常见问题"

msgid ""
"- **Q: Startup fails with HCCL port conflicts (address already bound). What "
"should I do?**"
msgstr "- **问：启动失败，提示HCCL端口冲突（地址已绑定）。该如何处理？**"

msgid "A: Clean up old processes and restart: `pkill -f VLLM*`."
msgstr "答：清理旧进程后重启：`pkill -f VLLM*`。"

msgid "- **Q: How to handle OOM or unstable startup?**"
msgstr "- **问：如何处理内存不足（OOM）或启动不稳定的情况？**"

msgid ""
"A: Reduce `--max-num-seqs` and `--max-model-len` first. If needed, reduce "
"concurrency and load-testing pressure (e.g., `max-concurrency` / `num-"
"prompts`)."
msgstr ""
"答：首先减小`--max-num-seqs`和`--max-model-len`。如有必要，降低并发度和负载测试压力（例如`max-"
"concurrency` / `num-prompts`）。"
